videos.headline: Eichel: 'We just weren't ready to play'
videos.description: Linda Cohn caught up with Sabres rookie Jack Eichel to talk about Buffalo's loss to Edmonton and the frustrations he faced playing No. 1 draft pick Connor McDavid.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Interview (Eichel: 'We just weren't ready to play') 2016/03/01
